HW6: textures and lighting


Dmitriy Tarasov
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2017

work in progress trebuchet

Key bindings
  "1"        enable/diable lighting   
  "2"        enabled/disable axes
  "3"        change between orthogonal and perspective
  "z"/"Z"    change ambient light
  "x"/"X"    change diffuse light
  "c"/"C"    change specural light
  "v"/"V"    change emission light
  "b"/"B"    change shininess
  "q"        rotate light source
  "["/"]"    change light in 
  "k"/"l"    change radius of rotation 
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
